thread.title: BRIEF-Euroinvestor.Com FY 2017 Revenue Dkk 63.2 mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Euroinvestor.Com FY 2017 Revenue Dkk 63.2 mln
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - EUROINVESTOR.COM A/S:
* FY 2017 REVENUE DKK 63.2 ‍​ MILLION VERSUS DKK 72.7 MILLION YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 EBIT LOSS DKK ‍​ 245,000 VERSUS PROFIT DKK 50.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* PROPOSES NO DIVIDEND FOR 2017 * EXPECTS FOR 2018 THAT GROUP‘S REVENUE WILL BE AT LEAST DKK 65 MILLION ( DKK 63.2 MILLION IN 2017)
* EXPECTS RESULT OF PRIMARY OPERATIONS 2018 AT LEAST AT DKK 13 MILLION VERSUS DKK 12.3 MILLION IN 2017‍​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
